    "question_id" : 5804043,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In addition to @Thilo's accepted answer, <code>Math.toIntExact</code> works also great in Optional method chaining, despite it accepts only an <code>int</code> as an argument</p>\n<pre><code>Long coolLong = null;\nInteger coolInt = Optional.ofNullable(coolLong).map(Math::toIntExact).orElse(0); //yields 0\n</code></pre>\n"
